- Killed a false number — "a Type 9 origin story in eleven words" matched neither quoted sentence; now "disguised as a shrug," which also echoes the "unbearably mild" deflection it points at.
- De-echoed "the only thing" (twice in the empathy turn) and "finally" (twice in the closer, so the Venice "finally" lands alone).
- Split the comeback mega-paragraph (Robotman → Brendanaissance) for mobile.

